@fg r=valkyrie_blue left=450 top=60
[texton]
[name n=Valkyrie f=valkyrie_blue_00]「This is the Mountain of the Gods... It is a mountain where the angel race, said to be the descendants of the gods, live...」[k]
[name n=Valkyrie f=valkyrie_blue_00]「Angels have large wings on their backs...[r] With these wings, they can float in the air even without magical powers...」[k]
[name n=Valkyrie f=valkyrie_blue_00]「It is said that the feathers dropped by angels and the feathered robes they wear possess mysterious powers...」[k]
[textoff]
@clf

[eventoff]
