;[exp] party.lastIsMove

@fg r=valkyrie_blue left=450 top=60
[texton]
[name n=Valkyrie f=valkyrie_blue_00]「We Valkyries have been entrusted by the angels with the task of protecting the Mountain of God on this earth.」[k]
[name n=Valkyrie f=valkyrie_blue_00]「The angels reside on the mountain. The Mountain of God is a sacred place where we earthly people are not allowed to enter.」[k]
[textoff]
